the company will distribute,"

38:30.833 --> 38:33.833
instead of "will be distributing."

38:41.833 --> 38:42.667
Fix it, then.

38:44.125 --> 38:44.958
Go ahead.

38:49.000 --> 38:50.167
Reading my contract?

38:50.250 --> 38:52.000
-No, Mr. Luca.
-Think I can't write?

38:52.083 --> 38:55.667
