44:48.458 --> 44:49.917
You're the big shot, right?

44:50.917 --> 44:51.833
Wanna kill him?

44:53.333 --> 44:54.292
Go kill him.

44:55.500 --> 44:57.833
Kill Luca, Nando, the lady at the bar.

44:59.708 --> 45:00.667
The cops.

45:01.625 --> 45:03.208
You'll have to kill them all.

45:04.833 --> 45:05.667
So?

45:06.708 --> 45:07.792
Who's first?

45:14.333 --> 45:15.167
Done.

45:20.167 --> 45:21.000
Got it.

45:21.750 --> 45:22.583
Take it out.

45:52.542 --> 45:55.000
Go! Come on, kid. Grab that thing.

45:56.583 --> 45:58.250
Go shower. We're going out.

46:00.250 --> 46:01.167
Go!

46:04.792 --> 46:06.333
Did you forget something?

46:06.833 --> 46:07.667
Go!

47:43.167 --> 47:44.542
-Hi, Luca.
-How are you?

47:44.625 --> 47:45.542
It's all good.

48:05.083 --> 48:05.917
Okay.

48:06.000 --> 48:07.875
On your feet! Come on.

48:09.125 --> 48:09.958
Let's go!

48:12.833 --> 48:14.625
These are Bolivian.

48:14.708 --> 48:15.708
Haitian.

48:16.292 --> 48:18.208
Venezuelan. Everybody's healthy.

48:20.375 --> 48:21.208
Hey, Big Luca!

48:22.125 --> 48:23.500
You wanted strong men?

48:28.375 --> 48:29.417
Pick three.

48:39.708 --> 48:40.625
It's up to you.

48:48.042 --> 48:50.000
-These three.
-Okay.

48:50.667 --> 48:53.333
Come on! Let's go! Go!

48:54.000 --> 48:55.458
Go!

48:56.583 --> 48:57.417
Walk.

48:58.042 --> 49:00.042
Here. Wait here!

49:01.750 --> 49:03.042
