49:03.875 --> 49:05.208
Shut up! Get in!

49:07.292 --> 49:08.625
Here, their passports.

49:14.458 --> 49:15.458
Let's go.

49:58.583 --> 50:01.292
Hey. What's up?

50:01.375 --> 50:02.208
Good.

50:06.625 --> 50:09.167
-So?
-Wow, you don't mess around.

50:11.542 --> 50:12.625
