They all sleep here…

50:27.958 --> 50:28.792
Come here.

50:30.542 --> 50:31.375
They're here.

50:35.250 --> 50:36.083
Let's go.

50:41.167 --> 50:43.000
-Sir, let me go.
-You two, come.

50:43.500 --> 50:45.708
