-Where are you taking me?

51:08.875 --> 51:09.708
Go!

51:09.792 --> 51:11.417
Help!

51:11.500 --> 51:12.542
Help!

51:12.625 --> 51:13.458
Get him!

51:20.333 --> 51:21.333
Bring him here.

51:25.167 --> 51:26.458
I'm gonna do something.

51:26.542 --> 51:28.583
If you try to escape,

51:28.667 --> 51:30.292
