51:36.625 --> 51:38.083
He understands it now.

51:38.667 --> 51:40.917
Big Luca, always a pleasure.

51:41.000 --> 51:43.417
-Let's go.
-You're good, kid.

51:44.125 --> 51:44.958
You're good.

52:25.542 --> 52:26.375
Take them.

52:28.083 --> 52:30.167
It's $10k each. Don't fuck around.

52:30.250 --> 52:33.083
-Come on. Go.
-Don't come back without the money.

52:45.375 --> 52:47.083
Who are you? Where's Luca?

52:47.667 --> 52:48.583
Where's Luca?

52:50.000 --> 52:51.375
He's downstairs.

52:51.458 --> 52:52.792
Go check downstairs.

52:52.875 --> 52:54.333
Go!

52:58.417 --> 52:59.667
